{
  "_comment": "ADR 0011 競争シグナル検証。adaptive-arb(競合 fee を見て勝てる最小限を機会価値内で積む) を 固定割合入札 greedy(0.6)/timid(0.2)/flat(0.0) と対戦させる。全 arb は同じ機会を取りに行く。仮説: adaptive は flat(積まなすぎ→front-run revert)と greedy(積みすぎ→fee 浪費)の両方を net で上回る = 競争シグナルが『適量入札』を計算可能にする。要 economicGas=1, ENABLED_PROTOCOLS=uniswap,balancer,curve, CROSS_VENUE_SPREAD_FLOW_MAX_WETH_WEI>0。",
  "agents": [
    {
      "id": "adaptive-arb",
      "command": "node",
      "args": ["--import", "tsx", "examples/agents/adaptive-arb.ts"],
      "wallet": "AUTO",
      "description": "競合 fee を見て勝てる最小限を機会価値内で積む(競争シグナル使用)"
    },
    {
      "id": "arb-greedy",
      "command": "node",
      "args": ["--import", "tsx", "examples/agents/arb-bot.ts"],
      "wallet": "AUTO",
      "env": { "BID_PROFIT_FRACTION": "0.6" },
      "description": "利益の60%を機械的に積む(過剰入札)"
    },
    {
      "id": "arb-timid",
      "command": "node",
      "args": ["--import", "tsx", "examples/agents/arb-bot.ts"],
      "wallet": "AUTO",
      "env": { "BID_PROFIT_FRACTION": "0.2" },
      "description": "利益の20%を機械的に積む"
    },
    {
      "id": "arb-flat",
      "command": "node",
      "args": ["--import", "tsx", "examples/agents/arb-bot.ts"],
      "wallet": "AUTO",
      "env": { "BID_PROFIT_FRACTION": "0.0" },
      "description": "入札しない(default fee)"
    },
    {
      "id": "noop",
      "command": "node",
      "args": ["--import", "tsx", "examples/agents/noop.ts"],
      "wallet": "AUTO",
      "baseline": true
    }
  ]
}
